{{Infobox Ukrainian raion | name = Krasnodonskyi Raion | Ukrainian_name = Краснодонський район | image_skyline = | image_shield = Krasnodonskyi rayon gerb.png | image_flag = Krasnodonskyi rayon prapor.png | image_map = Krasnodonskyi-Raion.png | mapsize = 250px | region = [[Luhansk Oblast]] | region_flag = {{flagicon|Luhansk Oblast}} | coordinates = {{coord|48|22|51|N|39|40|36|E|type:adm2nd_region:UA|display=inline,title}} | city_councils = 0 | town_councils = 5 | village_councils = 10 | villages = 47 | settlements = | date_created = 1938 | population = {{decrease}} 29,691 | population_as_of = 2013 | area_km2 = 100 | elevation_m = | admin_center = [[Krasnodon]] | governor = Oleksandr Kravtsov | raion_phone_code = 6462 | postal_index = 94415—94493 | website = https://web.archive.org/web/20140223013950/http://kd.loga.gov.ua/ }} '''Krasnodon Raion''' ({{Lang-uk|Краснодонський район}}) is a [[raion]] (district) in [[Luhansk Oblast]] of eastern [[Ukraine]]. The administrative center of the district is the city of [[Krasnodon]], which is incorporated separately as the [[city of regional significance (Ukraine)|city of oblast significance]] and does not belong to the raion. Population: {{Ua-pop-est2013|29,691}}.
